Hmm.. today. Today has been well.. fun.. if you could call it now. I'm still at school so i'll give you the best update i can manage for now..

1st lesson was tech. That was fun.. ok let me explain, half of our year has gone bowling but cause Hayleigh couldn't make it i offered to not go and stay behind with her so she wasn't alone. The whole group - bar Hayleigh and I - went. SO we had to do normal lesson. Fun.. Anyway first lesson was actually quite fun. We did make up on each other and Ruth massaged my back. (Tom: you know that huge tension knot i have on my left shoulder? Well she felt it and went "bloody hell!") She'd tried to get rid of it. She said she heard it pop. IT HURT! I kept wriggerling so it made her press harder. Ouch! That lesson seemed to take ages to end.. but it ended. Finally. 

2nd was maths. MATHS SHOULD BURN IN HELL! 'nuff said

Break was ok. we went into the music block. Hayleighus played me her piece on the piano.. t'was good. 

3rd was Science and we watched and educational video on DNA. When teacher turned it off Jenny yelled across the class 2aww miss i was just getting into that" and looked disapionted. hehehe.. i love jenny! i spent the rest of the lesson talking to antonio and stuart about piercings and for some reason my trousers falling down.. oO 

i actually ate lunch today. heh.. big news! i couldnt eat all of it but at least i tried.. *shrugs*

4th was RE. boringgg.. we kept getting told off for messing around. then leoni pretended that she couldn't bend her leg. She kept waving it around. hehe.. mariza, hayleigh and me couldnt stop laughing at her. it was great *grins*

we went up to registration and boyle got told off by mr dixon. that boy is trouble.. :P

5th was english and we watched a video. i was sat with rose *hearts rose* that was funny. we kept making fun of it. 

its the end of the day and im in ict with Sam, Ben and Marcus.. *waves*

anyway best go. this is the best update i've done in donkeys.. be proud..

oh yeah i'm going out for a meal tonight with work *grins* i get to see su *bounces* t'is a good reason to dress up. i'll try and take a picture for you lot..

squeaky chairs are fun..

love you all xx

reflection, and wisdom. They are governed by
the goddess Persephone and their sign is The

may be hard on yourself. You probably have
been hurt in the past by other people and can
sometimes distance yourself, as a result. You
don't usually let other get too close to you,
but you are very good at mending your spirits
back together by yourself.
